edu.harvard.integer.common

Class ID

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.common.ID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDInterface, java.io.Serializable

    @Embeddable
public class ID
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDInterface, java.io.Serializable
    This class is used to pass the identifier of a data object in the Integer system. The name and type are included so the GUI can display the object correctly and allows for a common way to ask for an object.
